headline: Arista Networks Is the S&P 500’s Top Stock Today. Why It’s Soaring Isn’t Clear.
summary: Arista Networks  stock spiked Thursday, though the catalyst for its big move wasn’t immediately clear.  Sell-side analysts told Barron’s Thursday they were still looking for a definitive trigger, but interest in the stock didn’t come out of nowhere, said Ryan Koontz of Needham & Co.
